WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:03.500
Look at this picture-lingling.

00:03.500 --> 00:06.200
This is my classroom.

00:06.200 --> 00:09.000
It's not big.

00:09.000 --> 00:13.000
There are 30 students in my class.

00:13.000 --> 00:19.100
16 are girls and 14 are boys.

00:19.100 --> 00:22.700
There are 30 desks in the classroom.

00:22.700 --> 00:26.900
And there are some books on the desks.

00:26.900 --> 00:31.400
On the teachers desk, there's a computer.

00:31.400 --> 00:37.900
There's also a television, but there isn't a map on the wall.

